column2: 1. Data between November 2005 to October 2010 have undergone Intercensal Adjustment after 2010 Population Census Result was available. 2. The intercensal adjustment is done by evenly distributing the differenence between the Population at Oct 1,2010, from 2010 Population Census and Original esitmates based on 2005 Population respectively, over the period November 2005 to October 2010.3. Intercensal Adjustment has only been made to Total Population, Total Male and Total Female Population. No adjustment has been made for the population by age.
column15:
1. Data prior to Jan-2016 are obtained through direct arrangement with Indonesia Cement Association. Data after Jan-2016 figure comes from alternative sources. The alternative sources only provide data for aggregates and do not include any information on the associated breakdown.
2. While the Indonesia Cement Association provided data up till January 2016, some of the 2015-2016 data are subsequently revised from alternative sources and as such, these figures may not tally with its associated breakdown.


1. Data sebelum Jan-2016 diperoleh melalui pengaturan langsung dengan Asosiasi Semen Indonesia. Data setelah Jan-2016 angka berasal dari sumber-sumber alternatif. Sumber alternatif hanya menyediakan data untuk agregat dan tidak mencakup informasi tentang perinciannya.
2. Sementara Asosiasi Semen Indonesia menyediakan data sampai Januari 2016, selanjutnya beberapa data tahun 2015-2016 direvisi dari sumber-sumber alternatif dan dengan demikian, angka-angka ini mungkin tidak cocok penghitugannya dengan rincian yang terkait.
